| 5ï¸âƒ£ | Palindrome check | `"madam"` â†’ Palindrome | Reverse & compare |  
```js
let str = "madam", rev = "";
for (let i = str.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) rev += str[i];
console.log(str === rev ? "Palindrome" : "Not");
``` |  
```ts
let str: string = "madam", rev: string = "";
for (let i: number = str.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) rev += str[i];
