| 8ï¸âƒ£ | Swap case | `"AbCdEf" â†’ "aBcDeF"` | Toggle case per character |  
```js
let str = "AbCdEf", res = "";
for (let ch of str) res += ch === ch.toUpperCase() ? ch.toLowerCase() : ch.toUpperCase();
console.log(res);
``` |  
```ts
let str: string = "AbCdEf", res: string = "";
for (let ch of str) res += ch === ch.toUpperCase() ? ch.toLowerCase() : ch.toUpperCase();
console.log(res);
``` |

