| 9ï¸âƒ£ | Reverse sentence words | `"I love testing" â†’ "testing love I"` | Split â†’ reverse loop |  
```js
let str = "I love testing", words = str.split(" "), res = "";
for (let i = words.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) res += words[i] + " ";
console.log(res.trim());
``` |  
```ts
let str: string = "I love testing"; let words: string[] = str.split(" "); let res: string = "";
for (let i: number = words.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) res += words[i] + " ";
console.log(res.trim());
``` |

