## ğŸ’¡ **Quick Loop Shortcut Memory:**

| Task Type | Start | End | Increment | Keyword |
|------------|--------|------|------------|-----------|
| Normal order | `i = 0` | `< length` | `i++` | â€œforwardâ€ |
| Reverse | `i = length - 1` | `>= 0` | `i--` | â€œbackwardâ€ |
| Two pointer | `i=length-1, j=0` | `i>=0` | `i--, j++` | â€œpairwiseâ€ |

